Name: 1 Residences
Краткая фраза: NEW 1 RESIDENCES LOCATED A FEW STEPS FROM ZABEEL PARK IN DUBAI
Description:
Surrounded by pristine waters on all sides, these beachfront apartments feature prominently on the Western Crescent of the Palm Jumeirah. W Residences Dubai offers one of the most prestigious addresses in the world. It offers 104 unique suites spread across eight majestic mansions with unobstructed, breathtaking views of the Arabian Gulf, Dubai's iconic skyline and Dubai Marina.

Crowning the top of Palma are five branded luxury penthouses that redefine the concept of spaciousness with 360° panoramic views. ‍

Name: Ahad Residences
Description: Ahad Residences is a 30-story residential building located in the heart of Business Bay. It includes studios, apartments with 1, 2 and 3 bedrooms. Ahad offers a unique living experience that allows residents to be part of a vibrant, modern and dynamic community. This project is being developed by AHAD Group and the contractor is Evan Lim-Penta, a well-known, reputable Singaporean developer who is actively involved in the project. They have built several high end projects in Dubai including Sofitel Palm Jumeirah and Saba Tower in JLT. They were recently recognized for their work on the Singapore, Netherlands and Sweden pavilions at Expo 2020.

Name: Ava at Palm
Description: The AVA at Palm Jumeirah luxury residential complex was launched in the 1st quarter of 2022 by one of the largest luxury real estate companies in Dubai - OMNIYAT. Throughout the long-awaited project, the main element is the water element, since the main entrance to the complex is decorated with endless reservoirs that intersect with each other, creating the impression of a unity of the building with the surrounding Persian Gulf. AVA at Palm Jumeirah features a total of 17 exclusive residences, including 3 and 4 bedroom apartments, as well as 1 duplex and 1 penthouse. The interiors of the residences will be designed by Portia Fox Design and will combine meticulous technical detail and inquisitive creativity. The ultra-modern 3 and 4 bedroom apartments overlooking the stunning Burj Al Arab and Ain Dubai will be from 660 to 813 square meters. m. They will be equipped with a private pool, a personal elevator, a maid's room and a family recreation area. In addition, for maximum convenience of residents, 3 parking spaces will be allocated for each unit of real estate.

Name: Avani Palm View Dubai Hotel & Suites
Address: На въезде на остров Palm Jumeirah
Description:
Palm Jumeirah Luxury ApartmentsPalm View on the Palm Jumeirah, offers ready-to-live-in 1 to 3 bedroom apartments with the ability to customize to your specifications.

It offers views of the Persian Gulf, the city skyline and Golf Views.Avani Palm View is a 48-story mixed-use building located in Al-Sufouh, at the entrance to Palm Jumeirah.

The project was launched in 2018 by Al-Fahim and has 264 units of properties, namely apartments with 1-3 bedrooms. All apartments are ready to move in, decorated in light colors, with marble floors, fully equipped kitchens, panoramic windows and private balconies. which include: a cafe and a 24-hour restaurant, a pool bar, a joint gym, parking, 24-hour security, as well as the possibility of individual finishing of the property

Name: Cavalli Tower
Краткая фраза: Cavalli Tower is divided into Luxury and Upper Luxury apartment types
Description:
Bringing runway glamor and glitz to private homes, Cavalli Tower is the result of a landmark collaboration between award-winning real estate developer DAMAC Properties and world-renowned fashion designer Roberto Cavalli. In fact, it is currently the only Cavalli-branded tower in the world that will make a splash among fans of ultra-luxury real estate. The grandiose complex will consist of 70 levels, where the interiors will be made according to an exclusive concept from the Italian brand Cavalli.

The cone-shaped architectural concept was created by Sean Killa, known for his innovative design for the long-awaited Museum of the Future in Dubai. Property buyers have an attractive opportunity to choose from a collection of branded 2-5 bedroom apartments overlooking the Persian Gulf, as well as penthouses of various layouts and sizes.

Name: CREST

Description:
The Crest Grande is a new residential project in Sobha Hartland, a very popular area with luxury real estate. The complex offers apartments with 1, 2, 3 and 4 bedrooms. The project is currently under construction with an estimated completion date of Q4 2025.

The Crest Grande is a crystal clear lagoon life and a wealth of amenities located on the waterfront in the heart of Dubai! Stylish, elegant and cosmopolitan lifestyle in the center Dubai, with a resort-style experience surrounded by unspoiled nature and water, as well as stunning views of the Dubai skyline and the world's largest tower, enjoying the waterfront, which is exclusive to residents of the Sobha Hartland community. Advantageous location, self-sufficient infrastructure - make The Crest Grande a great place to live, both for young couples and families with children.

Name: Lagoons
Краткая фраза: Lagoons is a new large-scale premium residential complex on the shore of an artificial lagoon in the prestigious Golf City area in Dubai, next to the golf course.
Description:
Lagoons is a new large-scale premium real estate complex, located among the lush greenery of the picturesque lagoons of the new Golf City in Dubai, a 15-minute drive from Dubai Marina and the beaches of the Persian Gulf.

The complex has easy access to Dubai's key highways including Mohammed Bin Zayed Road, Hessa Street, Emirates Road and Al Khail Road. crystal lagoons.

According to the general developer, the new project plans to be the same size as the nearby popular Damas Hills community, which has an area of ​​42 million square meters. f.

Name: MBL Residence Tower
Краткая фраза: MBL Residence is a premium multifunctional residential complex located in a developing family area in Dubai
Description:
MBL Residence is a premium multifunctional residential complex located in the emerging Jumeirah Lake Towers family district of Dubai. The building is a 40-story skyscraper, which houses 472 residential units. MBL Residence properties include one, two and three bedroom apartments ranging from 71-128 sqm. m. All objects are equipped with panoramic windows overlooking the pool, lake and cityscape. There are fully equipped kitchens and bathrooms with modern fixtures. The cost of housing is from AED 1,060,000 (USD 288,600).

MBL Residence is built in the popular cozy Jumeirah Lake Towers area, next to the picturesque park area. Residents of the complex have access to the major highway Sheikh Zayed Road. Within a 10-minute drive from the complex is the popular Dubai Marina resort area, with the shopping center of the same name, a yacht club and a promenade.

Name: MBL ROYAL
Краткая фраза: Residence is a new premium high-rise residential complex located on the lakefront in the Jumeirah Lake Towers area

Name: Mr. C Residences
Краткая фраза: Serviced apartments and penthouses located in the heart of Dubai Jumeirah!
Description:
Mr. C Residences Jumeirah is located just a short drive from downtown Dubai and the Jumeirah beach area, offering residents access to both sides of one of the world's most innovative cities.

Beaches and boating are within reach of residents, while multicultural and Italian restaurants and places to socialize are just steps away from their home.

Mr.C Residences is a modern waterfront residential complex that provides European comfort and luxury living in Dubai . The complex is located in the heart of the Jumeirah area and is currently under construction with an estimated completion date of Q4 2023. Mr.C Residences offers 3 and 4 bedroom apartments as well as three exclusive 5 bedroom penthouses.

Name: Orania
Краткая фраза: Orania Townhouses is a new 4th phase of The Valley residential complex, conveniently located next to Al Ain Road and Dubailand.
Description:
The village is located between the intersection of Al Ain and Jebel Ali Lehbab streets. Al Ain Road is the main traffic artery connecting the Al Ain area with Dubai, which means that The Valley can be an ideal place to move for those who already live in Al Ain and work in Dubai. With an affordable price, this is perhaps one of the best solutions to stay within a reasonable budget, but live in a green, secluded area that is closer to the center of Dubai than you think. The Valley is located away from the bustling urban areas.

However, the community is not without city advantages and is just a few steps away from Dubai Outlet Mall - the only place of its kind in the UAE where you can buy discounted goods from popular branded retail stores. Along with shopping, this establishment offers a wide range of entertainment and catering establishments. Rugby Sevens Stadium is another important complex nearby (10 minutes by car). It is regarded as one of the oldest and best rugby clubs in Dubai and hosts a three day rugby competition every year.

Name: Palme Couture Residences
Краткая фраза: Luxury here at the Palm Jumeirah
Description:
If you want something truly exclusive and impeccable in design, you need to check out Palme Couture. The design of these 14 residences is unmatched by any other complex in Dubai. Paying close attention to views, nature, light and balance, Palme Couture offers a truly high quality finish. There are very few apartments left in this designer complex. It is designed by Massimo Lisotti of Innovate Living.

Palme Couture for those who want to make Dubai their home. The 14 residences are divided into: - seven 3-bedroom apartments - two 4-bedroom apartments - two 4-bedroom townhouses with outdoor pools - two 5-bedroom duplexes with indoor/outdoor pools - 4-bedroom royal penthouse, 3-bedroom detached guest house and a rooftop pool. All these apartments will be fully serviced by 5 star hotel service.

Name: Peninsula
Краткая фраза: An oasis-inspired complex flanked by the Dubai Canal, promoting a luxurious lifestyle
Description:
A luxury complex with first-class amenities - Peninsula, washed from three sides by the Dubai Canal, is located in the most popular area of ​​​​Business Bay. A unique project for Dubai - plunge into the atmosphere of family comfort, without losing the opportunity to live in the city center - Downtown District. Peninsula will be your home. The main feature is the striking waterfront with famous restaurants, cozy cafes, beauty salons and shopping areas, which continues to parks, gardens and squares along the entire Dubai Canal.

An amazingly planned community with its own infrastructure and RTA Marine water taxi services. The Peninsula sets the standard for living in the heart of Dubai. Exercise, dine at the finest restaurants, go to the sea at any time, visit the boutiques of the world's prestige brands - Peninsula has it all. Located in the heart of the Business Bay area, the complex is ideal for business trips or planned holidays. You and your family will be impressed by the thriving environment of our community.

‍

Name: Safa One
Краткая фраза: New exclusive project - Safa One de GRISOGONO - The Nature of Luxury.
Description:
New exclusive project - Safa One de GRISOGONO - The Nature of Luxury. It will consist of two high-rise buildings designed in collaboration with the famous Swiss jewelry brand de GRISOGONO. The complex will be located on the border of the Safa Park, which will provide local residents with a beautiful view of the Dubai Canal and the Sheikh Zayed Road.

The architectural style of the buildings follows the outline of the masterpiece necklace created by the founder of the de GRISOGONO jewelry house, Fawaz Gruosi. The facade of the towers will be done in a deep royal shade of emerald green, which will become the signature style of the ultra luxurious Safa One project.

‍

Name: Safa Two
Address: Al Safa, Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Краткая фраза: Luxurious apartments on Sheikh Zayed Road
Description:
Safa TWO is a new luxury residential complex in the Al Safa area from Dubai's leading developer DAMAC Properties. The Safa project consists of two towers with a height of 44 and 60 floors, which will house luxury and ultra-luxury apartments with 1-3 bedrooms ranging from 78 to 139 square meters. m, as well as exclusive penthouses with 5 bedrooms. The residences were designed by the world-famous jewelry brand De Grisogono.

The complex will be built on the last plot available for development in Safa Park, a green reserve with an area of ​​64 hectares. Residents of Safa Two will be able to enjoy a peaceful life in nature, while being in close proximity to the most popular areas of the metropolis, such as Business Bay, Downtown Dubai and Jumeirah. Completion of the complex is scheduled for 2026.

The choice of apartments includes studios, 1 bedroom, 2 bedrooms and 3 bedrooms. The area of ​​residential apartments starts from 41 sq. m., and the cost is from $ 256,500. Studios and apartments are equipped with multifunctional furniture. Stunning design of the Tower and suites.

Name: Seven Palm
Краткая фраза: Imagine that you live just 5 minutes from the country's main thoroughfare - the Sheikh Zayed Highway.
Description:
Imagine that you live just 5 minutes from the country's main thoroughfare - the Sheikh Zayed Highway. Dubai International Airport is only 35 minutes and Expo2020 is 40 minutes away.

Comfortable layouts and modern interiors Seven Palm consists of two buildings - South and North residences, a suspension bridge with a terrace and a swimming pool and green parks around. Apartment types include Studios, 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments, as well as duplex penthouses with a huge terrace, private pool and stunning ocean views.

The elegant apartments are fully furnished in a modern style with panoramic windows to maximize daylight. Seven Palm is an exclusive and very special project

‍

Name: Six Senses
Краткая фраза: Luxurious residences in a new luxury complex in Dubai Six Senses The Palm.
Description:
The construction of the hotel and premium residences begins in January 2022, but Six Senses The Palm has already become the most highly anticipated project in the emirate. In total, the complex will have 60 hotel rooms and 162 ultra-luxury residences, including 121 penthouses, 32 sky villas and 9 beach villas. All buildings will have underground parking spaces and each villa will have its own garage.

Residents will be able to enjoy a wide range of hotel services, such as a gym, squash court, spa, library, conference rooms, kids club, beach area, swimming pools, restaurants, bars and much more. To maintain an active lifestyle, wellness and longevity centers, tennis courts, paddle courts and jogging tracks will be at your complete disposal. One of the highlights of Six Senses The Palm is a central garden with hills, also known as jebels, valley paths and patios. Six Senses The Palm's design will be modeled and influenced by coral, one of the region's most famous and sought-after natural resources.

Name: Sobha Hartland
Краткая фраза: Inspiring lifestyle, comfort and luxury in every detail - we have come closer to perfection than anyone else.
Description:
Sobha Hartland - a comfortable residential complex on the waterfront consists of luxury apartments, beautiful villas and luxury townhouses. Homes are surrounded by lush green spaces, world-class amenities and plenty of places for quality leisure.

Parks, international schools, shopping and entertainment complexes, cafes and restaurants - a real community center in the heart of Dubai. RESIDENTIAL COMPLEX IN THE HEART OF DUBAI - 12 MINUTES FROM THE BURJ KHALIFA, 20 MINUTES FROM THE INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT

Name: W Residesces
Краткая фраза: Apartments with stunning views of the coastline of Dubai and the Persian Gulf!
Description:
W Residences is a residential complex of 8 mansions with 104 apartments on the artificial island of Palm Jumeirah.

The facade of the house is made in a minimalist style with panoramic windows and spacious outdoor terraces. In the complex you can choose apartments with 2, 3. 4 and 5 bedrooms with terraces or private garden and pool. Penthouses with a ceiling height of 6.5 meters have separate lobbies and a private elevator. A 24-hour concierge will meet you in the common lobby, and a limousine service with a personal driver will help you get to anywhere in Dubai. On the territory of the complex there is a picturesque garden with cozy alleys, walking paths and closed gazebos for relaxation. It offers residents a private club with a private beach, a swimming pool and a picnic and barbecue area.

You can work out at the fitness center, play tennis with friends, and young residents will have fun on the playgrounds. For a nice family dinner or an interesting event, you can visit the nearby five-star hotel W Dubai - The Palm.
